      <description>taunt is only useful if the mob is &lt;b&gt;not&lt;/b&gt; attacking you.</description>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Apr 2006 04:07:42 GMT</pubDate>
      <author>FennyX</author>
      <guid>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=warriorbalance&amp;message.id=16800#M16800</guid>
